div.div: センスレス・ワンダー[ReREC]
Add project name to archive command + category id to create command

Fix bugs + Add features
- Give SuperAdmin users the ability to give/remove the SuperAdmin role - Fixed user page not updating immediately after SuperAdmin modifies a user (Bug with subscription) - Fix double project member creation on joining an open project - Keep join project button disabled after clicking to prevent multiple join requests - Change security context cache system to clear a user's security context cache rather than regenerating their cache on the subscription - Fix invalid project ObjectID on project page causing frontend to hang
